{"id": "1487511891634032841", "channel_id": "1487511891634032841", "type": 0, "author_id": "551488355821682688", "author_name": "eret.dashie", "author_bot": false, "content": "My friend has a bug where he can't skip the story. He tried restarting the game, but it didn't help. It doesn't work on all levels. The funniest thing is that all the other buttons work. Either this is cutting-edge technology forcing you to read the story, or it's a bug.", "timestamp": "2026-03-28T18:01:11.600000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1487511891634032841", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Skip button isn't working on Mobile", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1487508365814005972", "channel_id": "1487508365814005972", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "This pure Chaos Kathi team with 3 +12 standard units - is not strong enough to beat Wave 1 Alert 4 with the Health Inflation of the past year.\n\nI find this sad as it means beginner players can't level up random teams and must use the OP new units that do a lot of damage. \n\nMaybe you should look at all the teams you are leaving behind by doubling up the health of enemies in DTides since Kathi was released.\n\nMy +12 level 70 Jenkins used to be able to clear Alert 4. She can't any longer. The enemies health is just too high for her.\n\nI know this is important to Light - the HP increase is creating brain drain as a lot of off meta teams are no longer viable.", "timestamp": "2026-03-28T17:47:10.979000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-28T17:49:08.266000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1487508366631637177", "filename": "Untitled.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 6752029, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1487508365814005972/1487508366631637177/Untitled.png?ex=69fb7e9f&is=69fa2d1f&hm=83b0211fb31a47d5cc7d7ce60461b8457ab9a3b7b4b7f4c6b2648e23b388e2db&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1487508365814005972", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Alert 4 has too much health now.", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
